and
halting
his
army
he
watched
the
Hellenes
passing
by.
Clearchos
led
them
two
abreast,
sometimes
marching
and
sometimes
halting.
As
long
as
the
leading
section
of
the
army
halted,
so
long
there
must
be
a
halt
through
the
whole
