to
a
boy.
Indeed,
doctors
even
burn
and
cut
for
one’s
good.
If
you
think
a
love
of
violence
made
me
do
it,
consider
that
now,
thank
God,
I
am
more
confident
than
then,
I
am
bolder
now
than
then,
I
drink
more
wine
now,
yet
I
strike
no-one:
for
I
see
you
all
in
fine
weather.
But
when
